{"title":"CentOS安装独立显卡驱动教程","uid":"1745cb968693e532f7b243651a9eb5fc","slug":"CentOS安装独立显卡驱动教程","date":"2022-01-18T17:04:35.000Z","updated":"2022-04-01T16:35:43.193Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/CentOS安装独立显卡驱动教程.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"CentOS安装独立显卡驱动教程\"><a href=\"#CentOS安装独立显卡驱动教程\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"CentOS安装独立显卡驱动教程\"></a>CentOS安装独立显卡驱动教程</h1><p>写在开头，因为centos系统的与众不同，导致此系统的驱动安装方式有别与其他的操作系统，而刚好最近有机器需要解决这方面的问题，故经过多方的尝试终于成功了，现写出这篇教程希望能帮到有需要的人。</p>\n<h2 id=\"准备工作\"><a href=\"#准备工作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"准备工作\"></a>准备工作</h2><p>清除缓存并更新，也可直接执行第三行代码</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">yum clean all\nyum makecache\nyum update<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>添加ELPepo源</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">rpm --import https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.elrepo.org&#x2F;RPM-GPG-KEY-elrepo.org\nyum install https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.elrepo.org&#x2F;elrepo-release-7.el7.elrepo.noarch.rpm<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>如果上面的失效了也可以去 <a href=\"http://elrepo.org/tiki/tiki-index.php\">ELPepo</a>官网获取最新版本</p>\n<p>安装必须的组件</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">yum install gcc kernel-devel kernel-headers<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>安装NVIDIA驱动检测</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">yum install nvidia-detect <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>安装完这些之后建议重启一下</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">reboot<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"下载显卡驱动\"><a href=\"#下载显卡驱动\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下载显卡驱动\"></a>下载显卡驱动</h2><p>开机之后我们先检测显卡驱动及型号</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">nvidia-detect -v<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>输入这行代码之后，会返还这样一段信息，记住返还的XXX.XX 这个数字，后面下载驱动会用到</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">This device requires the current 470.86 NVIDIA driver kmod-nvidia<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>然后我们就可以去官网下载对应版本的驱动了 下载地址：<a href=\"https://www.geforce.cn/drivers\">https://www.geforce.cn/drivers</a> </p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">wget -r -np -nd（在后面加下载链接即可终端下载）<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>下载完成后，右键驱动包 先查看驱动的路径，路径不要有中文，有的话移动到没有的路径下，记住之后要用到，驱动包名同时也要记住</p>\n<h2 id=\"开始安装\"><a href=\"#开始安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"开始安装\"></a>开始安装</h2><p>然后我们先关闭图形界面</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">init 3<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>接着登入root账户</p>\n<p> 进入root账户后，cd进入下载的驱动目录下（就是刚刚叫你记住的路径）</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">cd &#x2F;home&#x2F;yxzk<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>给安装包权限然后运行开始安装,依次输入下面两行代码，这两行代码后面要改成自己下载的驱动包名</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">chmod +x NVIDIA-Linux-x86_64-470.86.run\nsh NVIDIA-Linux-x86_64-470.86.run<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>接下来便会开始安装，中间如果出现提示yes或no选项的选yes即可</p>\n<h2 id=\"安装完成\"><a href=\"#安装完成\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装完成\"></a>安装完成</h2><p>完成之后可以运行命令查看显卡状态</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">nvidia-smi<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>切回图形界面</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">init 5<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"附加\"><a href=\"#附加\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"附加\"></a>附加</h2><p>如果出现问题，可以用这段代码卸载显卡驱动</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">yum remove *nvidia*<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n","feature":true,"text":"CentOS安装独立显卡驱动教程写在开头，因为centos系统的与众不同，导致此系统的驱动安装方式有别与其他的操作系统，而刚好最近有机器需要解决这方面的问题，故经过多方的尝试终于成功了，现写出这篇教程希望能帮到有需要的人。 准备工作清除缓存并更新，也可直接执行第三行代码 yum ...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.1k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"教程","slug":"教程","count":2,"path":"api/categories/教程.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"CentOS","slug":"CentOS","count":2,"path":"api/tags/CentOS.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#CentOS%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E6%98%BE%E5%8D%A1%E9%A9%B1%E5%8A%A8%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">CentOS安装独立显卡驱动教程</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%87%86%E5%A4%87%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">准备工作</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E6%98%BE%E5%8D%A1%E9%A9%B1%E5%8A%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">下载显卡驱动</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\"><span class=\"toc-text\">开始安装</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90\"><span class=\"toc-text\">安装完成</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%99%84%E5%8A%A0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">附加</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"伍只小强","slug":"blog-author","avatar"